>> time required: 20 minutes
>> course: entre

Place sliced @cucumber{1%small} in a #colander, with @salt{1%tbsp}
Set aside for ~{30%minutes}
Rinse and squeeze dry
Place cucumber in bowl with sliced @shallots{0.33%cups}, chopped @green chili{1}, chopped @red chili{1}, @salt{0.5%tsp} and mix
Pour juice of @lime{1} and @coconut milk{2%tbsp}
Add crushed @bonito flakes{1%tbsp}
Mix and serve
